reviewText: You can play this DVD and entertain a house full of salsa lovers.  Can go wrong just pop it in and enjoy!!
I bought this for my b'day...it came....everything was great...love this...there are a couple of songs I don't remember seeing in the soap opera-I would highly recommend this to everyone!!!
Full of great songs like the first disc. Tough choice if you just want one they are both good! Would be good to listen to at any party.
